{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_76","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"sed -n '1,220p' PR_COMMENTS.md\"","aggregated_output":"This change addresses issue `#3591` by reclassifying `UBERON:0001629` (`carotid body`) away from the carotid arterial tree and under the peripheral nervous system.\n\nRationale:\n- The current issue correctly notes that the carotid body is a sensory organ of the peripheral nervous system rather than a structural part of `common carotid artery plus branches`.\n- The cited source, `PMID:32965908`, describes the carotid body as a peripheral nervous system sensory organ located in the adventitia at the bifurcation of the common carotid artery. I used that to support both the revised text definition and the new parentage.\n\nChanges made:\n- Removed `relationship: part_of UBERON:0001530 ! common carotid artery plus branches`.\n- Added `relationship: part_of UBERON:0000010 ! peripheral nervous system`.\n- Revised the definition to explicitly describe the carotid body as a sensory organ of the peripheral nervous system and added `PMID:32965908` as a definition xref.\n- Added `property_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3591\" xsd:anyURI`.\n\nValidation and checks completed:\n- Reviewed the imported issue context and the cited PMID record.\n- Checked the existing local stanzas for `UBERON:0001629`, `UBERON:0001530`, `UBERON:0034978`, `UBERON:0034979`, and `UBERON:0000010` before editing.\n- Edited via `obo-checkout.pl` / `obo-checkin.pl` rather than modifying the large edit file directly.\n- Reserialized `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` with `robot convert -i src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo -f obo -o src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`.\n- Restored unrelated serialization-only diffs so the final commit stays scoped to the carotid body fix.\n\nCompleted checklist:\n- [x] Confirm issue scope from `__issue_context__.json`\n- [x] Review cited literature support\n- [x] Verify the replacement parent term in the local ontology\n- [x] Update the term classification and metadata\n- [x] Re-serialize and inspect the final diff\n\nCommit:\n- `bec655e` `Reclassify carotid body under peripheral nervous system`\n\n@dragon-ai-agent\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
